rplespot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#8E9173>4/18/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#8E9173>7:52:53 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: PoH 15/4 recap</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">One minor correction, Mananin. She was awarded the next drop not because she didn't want the piece, but because it was looted in error by another person due to my own mistake. Her not getting the original piece was my fault, not hers. Therefore, as the winner of the lotto, she was give the next piece that dropped if she did not already have that piece. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
