</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#FFFFCC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uflarrenlagdalen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Flarren Lagdalen</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#8E9173>4/18/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#8E9173>10:42:34 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: PoH 15/4 recap</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I see both points but I agree with Mananin to a degree. If there was a regular piece on the high priest that should have been the piece she won. afterall god loot is still god loot and I'd be whoppin mad if a mistake happened and I didn't get my one in a million shot at my epic too. But past is past granted.<br>
Right now all of FoF is going over the rules set out by SB for the raids they held and are making minimal course corrections here and there. One we are all strong on is that the BP, legs and God loot be all 1 roll. No one should be able to walk away with possibly all 3 in 1 night we feel so thats a probability for ammendment. We'll post a list of the original rules and our revised ones when we're ready.<br>
<br>
PS. we would start running raids right away but our guild leader lost his isp (they went bankrupt) and he asked us to wait for him.<br>
<br>
Lagdalen Tarcho &lt;Fellowship of Faydark&gt;<br>
51 Elementalist Officer</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#CBC6B1><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uvalherji.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valherji</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#8E9173>4/18/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#8E9173>11:01:27 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: PoH 15/4 recap</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I heard you all fought the Magi (drops the Mage earth staff). Could anyone post details of the fight? How hard was he, what was he hitting for, what was he casting, etc. etc. etc. Any info would be great, thanks.<br>
